These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: western, martial-arts, sports, horror, animation, disaster, scientific
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, baseball, biathlon, cycling, parkour, skiing, volleyball
 1. the person watching western movies is between the person watching horror movies and the person watching scientific movies##2
 2. the person watching martial-arts movies is in the middle##1
 3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person watching animation movies is between the person who's sport is biathlon and the person who's sport is parkour##2
 5. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1
 6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 7. the person who's sport is badminton is between the person who's sport is cycling and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person watching animation movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
10. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
11. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3    |     4     |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | western | scientific | martial-arts    | sports | animation   | disaster    |
| Sport         | skiing  | baseball   | cycling | badminton | biathlon   | volleyball | parkour |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-2::.
7 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, rat, guinea-pig, mouse, dog, frog
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, italian, pakistani, polish, russian, turkish
1. the russian is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the rat is between the owner of the dog and the russian##2
3. the chinese is on the right of the australian##1
4. the owner of the frog is on the right of the italian##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is in the middle##1
6. the polish is on the left of the australian##1
7. the turkish is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
8. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the pakistani##1
9. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |      3      |      4      |    5    |     6      |    7    |
| Pet          | mouse | rat | dog | hedgehog | frog | cat      | guinea-pig  |
| Nationality   | russian | pakistani  | turkish     | italian     | polish  | australian | chinese |

