.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-4::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: country, disco, electronic, gospel, hip-hop, indie, trance
There are 7 different nationalities: australian, chinese, malaysian, mexican, nigerian, pakistani, polish
 1. the fan of trance is on the left of the malaysian##1
 2. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the nigerian##1
 3. the pakistani is on the right of the mexican##1
 4. the fan of hip-hop is on the right of the nigerian##1
 5. the australian is on the right of the fan of country##1
 6. the mexican is between the fan of electronic and the pakistani##2
 7. the fan of country is in the middle##1
 8. the mexican is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
 9. the fan of disco is the chinese##1
10. the australian is the fan of trance##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |   4    |     5      |     6     |    7     |
| Music-Genre      | electronic    | hip-hop  | gospel  | country  | trance      | indie       | disco |
| Nationality   | nigerian | mexican | pakistani | polish | australian | malaysian | chinese  |

