.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-5::.
City: san-francisco, edinburgh, hannover, colone, boston, liverpool, nizza
The people use 7 different means of transport: bike, helicopter, motorbike, ship, skateboard, train, van
1. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
3. the person driving the bike is between the person traveling to nizza and the person traveling to san-francisco##2
4. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
5. the person driving the bike is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is the person traveling to colone##1
9. the person traveling to boston is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2   |     3     |  4   |     5     |     6      |  7   |
| City   | colone      | boston | san-francisco | hannover | nizza      | edinburgh      | liverpool |
| Transport     | helicopter | train | van       | bike | motorbike | skateboard | ship |

