3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1
5. the person who growstulip is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who growszinnia##2
7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
8. the person who growstulip is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |      2      |        3        |      4       |     5     |     6     |   7    |
| Flower     | lily | zinnia | aconite | tulip | poppy | begonia     | azalea |
| Sport   | cycling   | lacrosse    | snowboarding    | parkour      | climbing  | badminton | rowing |

