.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: soul, gospel, metal, r&b, pop, country, ambient
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: cricket, cycling, parkour, rowing, rugby, surfing, volleyball
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is the fan of pop##1
