 3. the person who's sport is cycling is in the middle##1
 4. the fan of metal is between the person who's sport is rugby and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
 5. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 6. the fan of soul is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 7. the person who's sport is rowing is the fan of soul##1
 8. the fan of country is the person who's sport is rugby##1
 9. the person who's sport is parkour is between the person who's sport is rugby and the fan of pop##2
10. the fan of metal is on the left of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |    4    |    5     |    6    |    7     |
| Music-Genre   | soul | gospel    | r&b | metal   | country | ambient    | pop |
| Sport      | rowing | cricket | volleyball    | cycling | rugby    | parkour | surfing  |

