The people have 7 different jobs:  accountant, dressmaker, fisherman, librarian, photographer, police-officer, software-developer
 1. the photographer is on the left of the librarian##1
 2. the accountant is on the left of the fisherman##1
 3. the police-officer is on the far left##1
 4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 5. the photographer is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 6. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the tram and the person driving the car##2
 7. the dressmaker is on the right of the police-officer##1
 8. the accountant is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
10. the person driving the snowmobile is between the person driving the car and the person driving the jet-ski##2
11. the photographer is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1        |     2      |      3       |     4     |         5          |     6      |     7     |
| Transport   | trike  | skateboard   | jet-ski         | snowmobile     | car              | boat    | tram     |
| Job        | police-officer | dressmaker | photographer | librarian | software-developer | accountant | fisherman |

