4. the palace house is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1
6. the modern house is between the person who's sport is tennis and the victorian house##2
7. the cottage house is between the art-deco house and the tower house##2
8. the tower house is on the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
9. the victorian house is on the left of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |       2       |     3      |       4       |    5    |     6      |       7       |
