 3. the person drinking sprite is between the owner of the bird and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking mirinda##2
 5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
 7. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
 8. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 9. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
10. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |      3      |   4    |    5    |   6   |    7     |
